<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>Service - 标签 - 咔咔不太卡的博客</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/tags/service/</link><description>Service - 标签 - 咔咔不太卡的博客</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://ksmaple.github.io/tags/service/" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Kubernetes</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%B1%82/%E8%BF%90%E7%BB%B4%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2/kubernetes/</link><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>咔咔</author><guid>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%B1%82/%E8%BF%90%E7%BB%B4%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2/kubernetes/</guid><description><![CDATA[<h1 id="kubernetes">Kubernetes</h1>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>核心结论</strong>：Kubernetes通过声明式API管理容器化应用，通过Pod、Service、Deployment等抽象提供自动化部署、弹性伸缩和自我修复能力，是容器编排的事实标准。</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h2 id="kubernetes通过控制循环实现声明式管理通过分层抽象简化容器编排">Kubernetes通过控制循环实现声明式管理，通过分层抽象简化容器编排</h2>
<h3 id="核心对象">核心对象</h3>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>对象</th>
          <th>职责</th>
          <th>说明</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>Pod</td>
          <td>最小调度单元</td>
          <td>包含一个或多个容器</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>Deployment</td>
          <td>无状态应用管理</td>
          <td>滚动更新、回滚、扩缩容</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>StatefulSet</td>
          <td>有状态应用管理</td>
          <td>稳定网络标识、有序部署</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>Service</td>
          <td>服务发现</td>
          <td>ClusterIP/NodePort/LoadBalancer</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>Ingress</td>
          <td>七层路由</td>
          <td>HTTP/HTTPS路由规则</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>ConfigMap/Secret</td>
          <td>配置管理</td>
          <td>配置与镜像分离</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>PV/PVC</td>
          <td>存储管理</td>
          <td>持久化存储抽象</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>HPA</td>
          <td>自动伸缩</td>
          <td>基于CPU/内存/自定义指标</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
