<h3 id="pod生命周期与探针">Pod生命周期与探针</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">Pending → Running → Succeeded/Failed/Unknown
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">探针类型：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">- LivenessProbe：容器是否存活，失败则重启
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">- ReadinessProbe：容器是否就绪，失败则从Service摘除
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">- StartupProbe：容器是否启动完成，替代Liveness的initialDelay</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<hr>
<h2 id="常见问题与误区">常见问题与误区</h2>
<h3 id="问题1pod频繁重启">问题1：Pod频繁重启</h3>
<p><strong>根因</strong>：LivenessProbe配置不当或应用启动慢
<strong>解决</strong>：调整探针参数、增加StartupProbe</p>]]></description></item></channel></rss>